Scan all installed AUR packages on the system

Usage: aur-scan system [OPTIONS]

Options:
      --rescan                 Re-fetch PKGBUILDs from AUR (instead of using cache)
      --cache-dir <CACHE_DIR>  Custom cache directory for PKGBUILDs
  -c, --config <CONFIG>        Configuration file path
  -s, --severity <SEVERITY>    Minimum severity to report [possible values: critical, high, medium, low, info]
  -v, --verbose                Enable verbose output
  -q, --quiet                  Quiet mode (only show findings)
  -h, --help                   Print help
